== What Is A Royal Castle? ==
A '''Royal Castle''' is a [[Real Estate]] that can be obtained if the Player is born as a [[Royalty|Royal]]. The '''Royal Castle's''' Size is 30br/32ba to 39br/40ba.

== Appearance ==
The '''Royal Castle''' has a large entrance With 2 towers, and 1 Building where the [[Royal family|Royal Family]] lives. It has Large stone/brick walls with windows to see the view or firing arrows. It has a blue hue, alongside 4 blue flags in the tower.

The Haunted One has a large moon on its background and bats surrounding it. It is very rusty.

== Obtainment ==
It Can be Obtained when the player is born as A [[Royalty|Royal]].

== Trivia ==

* The '''Royal Castle''' is one of the buildings that can only be obtained trough [[Royalty]].
* It cannot be sold, added amenities, or rented.
* But Players can still throw a party at the castle.
* It also has the same activities and options as the Royal Palace.